Vestron to Declare Bankruptcy: Vestron Inc., once considered a high flier in 
the home-video business, said it will file for bankruptcy as part of a deal in 
which it will be acquired by Live Entertainment Inc., a diversified 
entertainment company. 
</P>
<P>
