FOREIGN RELATIONS -- KUWAIT; IRAQ -- ARMED FORCES -- KUWAIT; MILITARY 
CONFRONTATIONS; REFUGEES -- KUWAIT; REFUGEES -- IRAQ; ASIANS -- JORDAN 
</P>
