SIMON &amp; ASSOCIATES; HOLLYWOOD HIGHLAND PARTNERS; HOLLYWOOD BOULEVARD; LOS 
ANGELES COMMUNITY REDEVELOPMENT AGENCY; HOLLYWOOD (CA) -- DEVELOPMENT AND 
REDEVELOPMENT; LOS ANGELES -- DEVELOPMENT AND REDEVELOPMENT; LOS ANGELES -- 
FINANCES 
</P>
