prosciutto. Abby Mandel entertains in the kitchen. L. KENT WHITEHEAD / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, Rice salad with artichokes and prosciutto makes an 
excellent starter kitchen-oriented parties. RICK MEYER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
