<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAN GABRIEL VALLEY DIGEST: PASADENA; 
</P>
<P>
GUIDELINES FOR ARTS GRANTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Guidelines to disperse $190,000 in city money to artists and art groups were 
approved by City Directors on Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
Under the guidelines, grants of $45,000, $7,500 and $5,000 will be awarded to 
nonprofit organizations in Pasadena. The amount of the grant is based on the 
size of the organization. Nine artistic fellowships of $5,000 each will be 
awarded to individual Pasadena artists. 
</P>
<P>
Applications will be accepted by the city's Arts Commission in visual arts, 
film and video, music, theater, dance, literary arts, and multidisciplinary 
efforts. 
</P>
</TEXT>
