<P>
BOARD UPGRADES COMPUTERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
City Directors voted Tuesday to upgrade their computer capabilities. 
</P>
<P>
Since 1987, some directors have struggled along with Hewlett-Packard personal 
computers models that are incompatible with much of the IBM software on the 
market. 
</P>
<P>
