<HEADLINE>
<P>
VARIETY ROAD 3-1 FAVORITE FOR CALIFORNIA CUP CLASSIC 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By BILL CHRISTINE 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Variety Road, a stallion who returns to the races between breeding seasons, has 
been established as a 3-1 favorite in the $300,000 Classic, the richest stake 
Saturday at Santa Anita on the inaugural California Cup card. 
</P>
<P>
Variety Road, whose three stake wins this year have come in Northern 
California, is a 7-year-old who has left training for the breeding shed in 
February the past two years. 
</P>
<P>
The California Cup is a seven-race, $1-million stakes program restricted to 
California-bred horses. Two other races on the program -- maiden events -- are 
also for Cal-breds. 
</P>
<P>
There were 85 horses entered for the stakes. Here's the lineup: 
</P>
<P>
Starter Handicap, $50,000, 3 year-olds and up, 1 1/8 miles -- Harry V., Power 
Base, Raketmensch, Scout of Fortune, Comical, Simply Famulous, I Can Do That, 
Great Event, Proper Rider, Meadow's Interco. 
</P>
<P>
Sprint, $150,000, 3-year-olds and up, six furlongs -- Summer Sale, Express It, 
Valley Land, Answer Do, Due to the King, Just Deeds, Pass the Blame, Valiant 
Pete, Sensational Star. 
</P>
<P>
Distaff, $150,000, 3-year-olds and up, fillies and mares, about 6 1/2 furlongs 
on turf -- Linda Card, Fly Gaelic, Shinko's Lass, Somethingmerry, Paper 
Princess, She's a V.P., Survive, Hasty Pasty, Gin Rummy Judy, Singing Pirate, 
Classy Vigora, Dot's L'Natural, Intercivet, T.V. of Crystal. 
</P>
<P>
Juvenile, $100,000, 2-year-olds, colts and geldings, 1 1/16 miles -- What a 
Spell, Crystal's Game, Mizter Interco, Jimjen, Pillaring, Thisonesforyoumike, 
Sew Predictable, Frosty Paws, Rally Run. 
</P>
<P>
Mile, $150,000, 3-year-olds and up, one mile on turf -- Agirlfrommars, Eratone, 
Gum, Shirkee, Cove Way, Bel's Starlet, No Commitment, Effusive Bounty, Noble 
Dr., Individualist, Zin, Eddie Champion. 
</P>
<P>
Classic, $300,000, 3-year-olds and up, 1 1/8 miles -- Bel Darling, Rocket 
Gibralter, Variety Road, Stylish Stud, Elegant Bargain, Bel Air Paster, Rob an 
Plunder, On the Menu, Serious Flight, Annual Date, He's a Saros, Toby Jug, 
Advocate Training, My Sonny Boy, Hawaiian Pass. 
</P>
<P>
Juvenile Fillies, $100,000, 2-year-old fillies, 1 1/16 miles -- Teach Us, Hit a 
Homer Honey, Nat's Lea, Number's Game, Simple Surprise, Perky Slew, Serious 
Toy, Dragonetta, Theresa's Pleasure, Teresa Mc, Spirited Susan, Cassie June, 
Brisa De Mar, Nikki's Baby, Ten Hail Marys, First To Advance. BILL CHRISTINE 
</P>
