structure, character, plot, voice, narrative hook, adaptations, blockbusters, 
the agent's role and selling to Hollywood. Cost is $85 and includes lunch and 
parking. 
</P>
<P>
Among the speakers will be novelists MacDonald Harris ("Hemingway's Suitcase"), 
